Luis Rego https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Luis_Rego 0 Luis Rego (born 30 May 1943) is a French actor, comedian, writer and director, of Portuguese origins. He was a founding member of music/comedy group Les Charlots which he left after a few years.
